00:00:19.280 --> 00:00:31.100
Place spinach leaves and water into a blender and blend for about 1 minute

00:00:56.960 --> 00:01:04.780
filter out the fibers and set aside 300CCs of the spinach juice

00:01:26.340 --> 00:01:36.400
Mix the spinach juice and other ingredients together to form a smooth dough

00:02:04.340 --> 00:02:09.900
Mix the spinach juice and other ingredients together to form a smooth dough

00:02:12.520 --> 00:02:18.940
knead it again for 1 minute then the dough will be ready to be used to make spinach noodles

00:02:25.200 --> 00:02:34.820
Boil a pot of water, roll the dough into long strips, flatten and break off small pieces

00:02:51.120 --> 00:03:03.100
boil to make gnocchi, or roll the dough out to a thin round sheet then slice into strips to make spinach noodles.

